    "Command": {
      "description": "Ewellix Command:",
      "raw": "# Ewellix Command:\n# Through encoder ticks or meters. Encoder ticks take priority.\n\n# Ticks:\n# Encoder ticks range from 0 to 865.\nint32 ticks\n\n# Meters:\n# Range from 0 to max_height defined by the model.\n# Distance will be even divided amongst actuators.\nfloat32 meters\n",
