TION_ALL=0x3020\nuint16 WDF_REMOTE_POSITION_ACTUATOR=0x3021\n\n# Executable Functions\nuint8 EF_NO_MOTION=0\nuint8 EF_IN=1\nuint8 EF_OUT=2\nuint8 EF_MEM1=3\nuint8 EF_MEM2=4\nuint8 EF_MEM3=5\nuint8 EF_MEM4=6\nuint8 EF_INTERMEDIATE_IN=7\nuint8 EF_INTERMEDIATE_OUT=8\nuint8 EF_REMOTE_POSITION=9\n\n---\nbool success\n\n",
